her two trusted aides,

291
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:14,130
have all entered Baihua Pavilion.

292
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:16,400
How long have they been in there?

293
00:11:16,400 --> 00:11:17,080
It must have been

294
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,360
sixteen to eighteen hours.

295
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:20,360
Heaven is truly helping our Zhang family.

296
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:22,040
Several hours outside

297
00:11:22,040 --> 00:11:24,300
is only one hour inside Baihua Pavilion.

298
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,600
Su Ningxue,

299
00:11:25,800 --> 00:11:27,080
you are truly fierce.

300
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:29,440
Baihua Pavilion threatened the lives of the guests,

301
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:31,320
only allowing the few of them to enter.

302
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:33,360
The Empress left the soldiers outside to guard,

303
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:35,290
and only took three people inside.

304
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:38,880
She certainly has the courage and responsibility of the late Emperor.

305
00:11:38,880 --> 00:11:39,800
What a pity.

306
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:42,320
You, Su Ningxue, are not my daughter.

307
00:11:42,400 --> 00:11:43,720
Otherwise,

308
00:11:43,880 --> 00:11:45,960
I wouldn't mind you being the Empress.

309
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:46,760
Mother,

310
00:11:46,760 --> 00:11:48,360
there is also some bad news.

311
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:50,650
My cousin Zhang Mu and Minister Lin

312
00:11:51,400 --> 00:11:53,000
are also in Baihua Pavilion.

313
00:11:53,280 --> 00:11:54,960
They seem to be hostages now.

314
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:55,760
What?

315
00:11:56,680 --> 00:11:57,880
Zhang Mu is there too?

316
00:11:58,360 --> 00:11:59,440
Please calm down, Mother.

317
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,960
I will find someone to figure out a way right now.

318
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:01,890
There's no need.

319
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:04,200
Once this demon realm is opened,

320
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,730
unless a winner is decided,

321
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:08,000
it is very difficult to break its rules.

322
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,040
Mu,

323
00:12:10,520 --> 00:12:12,640
I hope heaven will bless you.

324
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:15,880
I wonder what kind of deal

325
00:12:15,880 --> 00:12:17,520
Young Master Lin wants to make

326
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:18,760
with me.

327
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:21,100
Tell me all the taboos of the first level.

328
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:21,840
We will

329
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,080
play with you.

330
00:12:25,920 --> 00:12:26,800
Young Master Lin,

331
00:12:26,800 --> 00:12:28,400
do you take me for a fool?

332
00:12:28,800 --> 00:12:30,400
You don't have to take a seat.

333
00:12:30,560 --> 00:12:31,760
I don't mind waiting.

334
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:39,960
The flow of time in the Hundred Flowers Pavilion

335
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:41,600
is already different from the outside world.

336
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:42,680
It's much faster here.

337
00:12:42,680 --> 00:12:43,320
How much

338
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:44,200
faster?

339
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:45,640
One hour here

340
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:47,960
is equivalent to three or four hours outside.

341
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:49,720
But the flow of time for our bodily functions

342
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:50,720
remains the same.

343
00:12:50,880 --> 00:12:52,120
Which means,

344
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:55,200
if we keep waiting,

345
00:12:55,280 --> 00:12:56,400
these guests

346
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:58,360
will soon die of starvation.

347
00:12:58,960 --> 00:12:59,640
Exactly.

348
00:13:00,120 --> 00:13:01,440
We have Qi-Restoring Pills,

349
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:02,970
but these commoners don't.

350
00:13:03,160 --> 00:13:04,240
I see.

351
00:13:04,680 --> 00:13:05,640
How vicious.

352
00:13:06,040 --> 00:13:06,760
However,

353
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:07,640
it's not a big problem.

354
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:08,280
Kid,

355
00:13:08,880 --> 00:13:10,000
it's best not to use

356
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:11,480
this parchment roll now.

357
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:13,400
This parchment roll is effective

358
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:14,480
for half an hour.

359
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:16,680
It should be used at the most critical moment.

360
00:13:16,680 --> 00:13:19,000
You haven't found the master of the Hundred Flowers Pavilion yet.

361
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,320
If you use it now,

362
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:22,880
she will realize the rules have been altered

363
00:13:22,880 --> 00:13:25,160
and prepare in advance.

364
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:28,320
Let's change the stakes.

365
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:30,600
You tell us all the rules and taboos,

366
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:32,720
and we won't attack you.

367
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:35,570
This young lady is even more reckless.

368
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:37,000
Didn't you see

369
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:38,860
what happened to the one just now?

370
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:41,160
I know Liu Wancai's temper best.

371
00:13:41,400 --> 00:13:42,880
He doesn't get angry easily.

372
00:13:42,880 --> 00:13:44,320
You used tricks

373
00:13:44,520 --> 00:13:45,920
to provoke his emotions

374
00:13:45,920 --> 00:13:47,380
and force him to act early.

375
00:13:47,560 --> 00:13:48,480
It was just

376
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:50,000
to force us apart,

377
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:50,920
right?

378
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:54,000
Liu Wancai was teleported somewhere else.

379
00:13:54,520 --> 00:13:55,320
That's right.

380
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:56,920
He should have been teleported

381
00:13:56,920 --> 00:13:58,080
to his own level.

382
00:13:58,840 --> 00:13:59,760
You three

383
00:13:59,760 --> 00:14:01,960
really make me look at you in a new light.

384
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,200
Cut the crap.

385
00:14:03,400 --> 00:14:04,520
Make a decision quickly.

386
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:05,200
Otherwise,

387
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:06,560
we will attack you together

388
00:14:06,560 --> 00:14:08,220
and then teleport to join him.

389
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:08,680
Wifey.

390
00:14:08,680 --> 00:14:09,640
Awesome.

